headline: Venue cancels a J.D. Vance campaign event after anger that Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene would join the meet-and-greet, report says
author: Joshua Zitser
sentences: Venue manager Jodi Taylor told the Enquirer that the venue was not aware that the politician from Georgia, who endorsed Vance in the Ohio Senate GOP primary on Tuesday, was featured as a special guest.
But on Thursday, the venue's management asked Vance's campaign to find another location after learning that it would feature controversial Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene, the Enquirer reported.
